headline: MetLife Q4 Earnings Beat Estimates on Increasing Volumes

headline: ICE's Q4 Earnings and Revenues Top Estimates, Dividend Raised
summary: ICE tops Q4 estimates as adjusted EPS rises 12.5% year over year, with record revenues and operating income driving a 1.9% pre-market stock gain.
